divs: Sighting DetailsI was taking photos of clouds, when I viewed them I noticed a strange object in the 2nd of a series of three. These were taken one after the other, seconds apart. This is how I know it is not a cloud formation or conventional craft. There was not enough time between photos for it to have been either. The first photo was taken at 3:02 pm the 2nd at 3:03 pm and the 3rd at 3:03 pm.
Summary: did not see UFO when i took 3 photos consecutively
